>>7dbceff0-d072-4263-ad8f-fb0b62cfea3c
You failed to address a huge annoyance. Galactichan will not accept .mkv posts.

This is a great bafflement, because webm uses the mkv container, and I know Millchan accepts H.264 mp4s.  So why is X264+AC3 inside an mkv container always a problem?

Recompression is NOT cost free. Millchan users need this fixed.
